## Build Base Hadoop
wget https://github.com/google/protobuf/releases/download/v2.5.0/protobuf-2.5.0.tar.gz
tar xfv protobuf-2.5.0.tar.gz
cd protobuf-2.5.0
./configure
make clean
make
make install
ldconfig
